      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. A great fit for buyers looking for straightforward value, it presents an opportunity to own a usable vehicle without overspending. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong affordability, this is a sensible choice for someone who appreciates honest, low-cost motoring.",
