    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great starter car, project, or handy runaround for the right buyer. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind, and for someone willing to give it a bit of TLC, there\u2019s real value here. If you want something affordable and straightforward, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with good fundamentals and real upside. The drivetrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of honest mechanical character that makes it a great budget entry for someone who appreciates a car with strong bones. Not a showpiece, but a usable driver with clear enthusiast potential\u2014ideal for someone looking for an affordable platform to sort, drive, and improve over time. Priced to reflect condition while still offering plenty of value for the right buyer.",
      "price": 6950.0,
