      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, well-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a machine with stories in its panels and plenty of life left for the next owner with a little vision. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who wants dependable daily-driver potential, a budget-friendly project, or simply an affordable set of wheels with personality you can\u2019t fake. If you appreciate a vehicle that feels seasoned rather than sterile, this one offers a rare chance to get into something memorable without stretching your budget.",
